{"tid":2427878,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"23歲李玹珠疑遭欺凌退出APRIL 友人證：隊友全是加害者","createTime":"2021-03-01T06:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T14:47:10.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cfb8adeb9eea94826e2fe056f2bf4493e4c41fa5","tid":2427878,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T06:21:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/laiy3ne-C-pjdQKJ23wz9NOfXMw=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SEVMS7PCOJFUTOCQRUX7VCE2RQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Flaiy3ne-C-pjdQKJ23wz9NOfXMw%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSEVMS7PCOJFUTOCQRUX7VCE2RQ.jpg&h=836fc1d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新增回應<br />\n<br />\n韓國女團AOA的27歲前成員珉娥，去年7月在網上控訴10年以來一直遭隊長智珉欺凌，不過昨日再有女團爆出欺凌事件，APRIL的23歲前成員李玹珠的胞弟昨日在網上發文，指姐姐因為遭隊友欺凌而患上恐慌障礙，一度試圖自殺，因此才退團，立即引起熱議。<br />\n<br />\n曾試圖自殺<br />\n自稱是李玹珠胞弟的網民表示，姐姐在隊內遭霸凌、排擠，因而患上恐慌障礙與呼吸困難，甚至試圖自殺，最後選擇退團，但事務所卻要求她在信中，表示是為了集中演技才退團，令姐姐被fans鬧她自私、背叛團體，長時間受到fans惡評攻擊。網民續指曾擔心爆料會影響到姐姐李玹珠的事業，所以一直忍耐，但看着APRIL成員像沒事一樣繼續活動、好好活着，再也不想袖手旁觀，所以才寫下了爆料文，他更直言：「連我都這麼痛苦，想到姐姐就更令我傷心及生氣。」<br />\n<br />\n同學加碼爆料<br />\n繼李玹珠胞弟發文後，自稱是李玹珠的高中同學亦加碼爆料，直指：「APRIL沒有旁觀者，全是加害者，只能說她們的欺負行為已經超出了單純忌妒的水準。」文中提到：「記憶中的玹珠是愛笑、可愛的朋友，雖然知道她受到欺凌依然堅持活動，卻只能給予安慰、一起生氣，沒有其他能做的，到現在才出現寫下這些內容，真的很抱歉。」<br />\n<br />\n對於網上爆料，APRIL所屬的DSP事務所僅在李玹珠胞弟發文後，表示「正在確認中」，之後就一直沉默，未有其他回應。APRIL於2015年出道，多次經歷成員變動，目前以6人之姿活動。李玹珠於2016年宣佈退團，轉型做演員。<br />\n<br />\n事務所否認<br />\n今日下午DSP事務所發聲明否認欺凌，指李玹珠本身是事務所的演員練習生，後來說服她加入April，但李玹珠出道後因為體力和精神上的問題而不能參與組合活動，翌年提出退團，當中並沒有加害者或受害者的存在。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Un6QIZWHYijHar4RjN_OO5DP38s=/802x962/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TGQD6WXSAVEWHEMK5U3WWNLF44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUn6QIZWHYijHar4RjN_OO5DP38s%3D%2F802x962%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTGQD6WXSAVEWHEMK5U3WWNLF44.jpg&h=0adfce56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_jzfuv0tVl2Fb8ELyqU_9GiT2dU=/802x1271/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LLRISZAJKFCCHA7AO3VWBGRHPQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_jzfuv0tVl2Fb8ELyqU_9GiT2dU%3D%2F802x1271%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLLRISZAJKFCCHA7AO3VWBGRHPQ.jpg&h=ad23970a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wNKdb9CrJkPSoZLpWKDDjczMgrc=/802x1437/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/J7OU7RR6OZG7PIXDM4UB74DRDE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwNKdb9CrJkPSoZLpWKDDjczMgrc%3D%2F802x1437%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJ7OU7RR6OZG7PIXDM4UB74DRDE.jpg&h=2839a775&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/o8BeRf1W8CE-QFKg8CWybl9aLoA=/802x532/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Q55TYT557REV3C37JTRDGORFXA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fo8BeRf1W8CE-QFKg8CWybl9aLoA%3D%2F802x532%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQ55TYT557REV3C37JTRDGORFXA.jpg&h=ee55fb8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210301/53JQBDK3TRBTXEDKR6MG6QIX5U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210301%2F53JQBDK3TRBTXEDKR6MG6QIX5U%2F&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3QXckNDuUEQQ0Md4EdtPbyE%3D&h=a0d5c7fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210301%2F53JQBDK3TRBTXEDKR6MG6QIX5U%2F&h=b9a25968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210301/53JQBDK3TRBTXEDKR6MG6QIX5U/</a>"},{"pid":"8c5de28751cd42596e57d8f54169eb73d7a5da01","tid":2427878,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T06:32:20.000Z","msg":"煩唔煩啲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日都蝦人 <br />\n唔同定仔都俾人蝦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c626fb6471d770d096d4b06042e45a7f0cfc952","tid":2427878,"uid":378793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T07:47:19.000Z","msg":"KARD入面果件有冇份？"},{"pid":"18964baf43151793173c619a4961719d203da380","tid":2427878,"uid":80047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T07:53:07.000Z","msg":"名都抄人唔方好人"},{"pid":"fe0ae19287613ef19da3621f13637dbf8bcf4dce","tid":2427878,"uid":71657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T07:56:59.000Z","msg":"邊隊kpop係無呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />爆唔爆出嚟咁解啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f2f500ed831bb683c6fd862cdb19c9e8ffc980","tid":2427878,"uid":312430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T14:47:10.000Z","msg":"t-ara no.2"}]}